HEADWORD: Potch
<hw>Potch</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <ety>[Cf. <er>Poach</er>
to stab.]</ety> <def>To thrust; to push.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
⟦ldquo⟧I 'll <xex>potch</xex> at him some way.⟦rdquo⟧
